{"scenario": "CLAR-03", "turn_index": 1, "variant": "less thinning", "request": {"message": "less thinning", "conversation_id": "72048b94-d580-4be6-8100-f5284c90e794"}, "response_body": {"response": "need to know where you're seeing the thinning. crown, temples, all over, or just noticing thinner strands overall. that said, the evidence-backed stack for slowing thinning is **finasteride** (blocks DHT, the hormone shrinking follicles) + **minoxidil** (stimulates growth and thickens strands). both require consistency over several months to show results. finasteride needs a doctor's sign-off. if you're early (just noticing it now), acting now beats waiting. thinning is way easier to slow early than to reverse later. what stage are you at. is it diffuse thinning across the whole scalp, crown thinning, or temple recession.", "choices": [], "multi_choice": false, "input_widget": null, "progress": null, "products": [{"name": "Kirkland Signature 5% Minoxidil Solution (6-month)", "brand": "Kirkland", "url": "https://www.amazon.com/Kirkland-Signature-5-Percent-Minoxidil-Solution-6-month/dp/B0DFVMQPDK", "description": "Generic 5% minoxidil liquid \u2014 same active as Rogaine, lower cost.", "image": ""}], "created_at": "2026-07-05T16:44:32.589438", "conversation_id": "72048b94-d580-4be6-8100-f5284c90e794", "confirm": null, "visual_blocks": [], "method_metadata": null}, "status_code": 200, "latency_s": 6.43, "transport_error": null, "checks": [{"name": "choices_absent", "passed": true, "detail": "choices=[]"}, {"name": "no_friendly_error", "passed": true, "detail": "clean"}, {"name": "prose_nonempty", "passed": true, "detail": "len=629"}, {"name": "latency_lt", "passed": true, "detail": "6.4s (ceiling 45s)"}, {"name": "no_reask", "passed": true, "detail": "no re-ask"}], "needs_judge": ["answers_the_question"], "turn_ok": true}
